Kernel Patches Required :
-----------------------
fanotfyd with feature FAN_REPORT_FID needs the kernel version after 5.9,
and needs to open kenrel config as below:
CONFIG_FSNOTIFY=y
CONFIG_FANOTIFY=y
CONFIG_FHANDLE=y

How to test :
-----------
$m fanotifyd
$adb push fanotifyd /system/bin/
$adb shell setenforce 0
$adb shell fanotifyd
